---
import DocsLayout from '../../components/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Framework Coverage" description="What pecto extracts from each language and framework.">

<h2>Java (Spring Boot + Jakarta EE)</h2>

<h3>Spring Boot Controllers</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Annotation</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@RestController</code> / <code>@Controller</code></td><td>Controller detection, capability name</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@RequestMapping("/path")</code></td><td>Base path for all endpoints</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@GetMapping</code>, <code>@PostMapping</code>, etc.</td><td>HTTP method + path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@RequestBody</code></td><td>Request body type + fields (cross-file)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@PathVariable</code></td><td>Path parameter name + type</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@RequestParam</code></td><td>Query parameter + required flag</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@ResponseStatus</code></td><td>Override success status code</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@ExceptionHandler</code></td><td>Error behaviors for all endpoints</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@PreAuthorize</code> / <code>@Secured</code></td><td>Roles and auth requirements</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@CrossOrigin</code></td><td>CORS configuration</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@RateLimiter</code></td><td>Rate limiting config</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Jakarta EE / JAX-RS Resources</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Annotation</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@Path("/api")</code></td><td>Resource detection (class or interface), base path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@GET</code>, <code>@POST</code>, <code>@PUT</code>, <code>@DELETE</code></td><td>HTTP method</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Path("/users")</code> on method</td><td>Method-level path (combined with base)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@PathParam("id")</code></td><td>Path parameter</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@QueryParam("status")</code></td><td>Query parameter</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Unannotated parameter</td><td>Request body (for POST/PUT)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@RolesAllowed("ADMIN")</code></td><td>Role-based security</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@PermitAll</code></td><td>Public endpoint (overrides class-level auth)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@DenyAll</code></td><td>Forbidden endpoint</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Jakarta EE Services</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Annotation</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@Stateless</code> / <code>@Stateful</code></td><td>EJB service detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@RequestScoped</code> / <code>@ApplicationScoped</code></td><td>CDI service detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Inject</code></td><td>Dependency injection (field-level)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@TransactionAttribute</code></td><td>Transaction propagation</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>em.persist()</code>, <code>em.merge()</code>, <code>em.remove()</code></td><td>EntityManager side effects</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Jakarta EE Repositories</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@PersistenceContext EntityManager</code></td><td>Repository detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td>extends <code>*Repository</code> base class</td><td>Repository detection + entity type from generic</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Public methods</td><td>Custom query operations</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Entities</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Annotation</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@Entity</code></td><td>Entity detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Table(name)</code></td><td>Table name</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Id</code>, <code>@GeneratedValue</code></td><td>Primary key constraints</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Column</code></td><td>Column constraints (unique, nullable, length)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@OneToMany</code>, <code>@ManyToOne</code>, etc.</td><td>Relationship type</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@NotNull</code>, <code>@NotBlank</code>, <code>@Email</code>, <code>@Size</code></td><td>Validation constraints</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Repositories</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>extends JpaRepository&lt;T, ID&gt;</code></td><td>Standard CRUD operations</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>extends CrudRepository</code></td><td>Standard CRUD operations</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>findByEmail(...)</code></td><td>Custom query: "Find by email"</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Query("SELECT ...")</code></td><td>JPQL/SQL query text</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Services</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Annotation</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@Service</code> / <code>@Component</code></td><td>Service detection, public methods</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Transactional</code></td><td>Transaction mode (required, read-only, requires-new)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>.save()</code>, <code>.delete()</code></td><td>DB side effects</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>publishEvent(new XxxEvent)</code></td><td>Event publishing side effects</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Scheduled Tasks</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Annotation</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@Scheduled(cron="...")</code></td><td>Cron expression</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Scheduled(fixedRate=N)</code></td><td>Polling interval</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@EventListener</code></td><td>Event type and handler</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="my-8 border-t border-gray-800/50"></div>

<h2>C# / .NET</h2>

<h3>ASP.NET Core Controllers</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>[ApiController]</code></td><td>Controller detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[Route("api/[controller]")]</code></td><td>Base path with template substitution</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[HttpGet]</code>, <code>[HttpPost]</code>, etc.</td><td>HTTP method + path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[FromBody]</code></td><td>Request body type + fields (cross-file)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[FromRoute]</code></td><td>Path parameter</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[FromQuery]</code></td><td>Query parameter</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[ProducesResponseType(StatusCodes.X)]</code></td><td>Response status + error behaviors</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[Authorize]</code> / <code>[AllowAnonymous]</code></td><td>Auth + roles</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>Task&lt;ActionResult&lt;T&gt;&gt;</code></td><td>Async return type unwrapping</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Entity Framework Core</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>[Table("name")]</code></td><td>Entity with table name</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[Key]</code></td><td>Primary key (also triggers entity detection)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>DbSet&lt;T&gt;</code> in DbContext</td><td>Entity type T resolved from context</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[Required]</code>, <code>[MaxLength]</code>, etc.</td><td>Validation constraints</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[ForeignKey]</code>, <code>[InverseProperty]</code></td><td>Relationship constraints</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>[NotMapped]</code></td><td>Property skipped</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Services</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Class name ends in <code>Service</code></td><td>Service detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Implements <code>I*Service</code></td><td>Service detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Constructor injection</td><td>Dependencies (IOrderService → order-service)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>SaveChangesAsync()</code></td><td>Transaction: unit-of-work</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>BeginTransactionAsync()</code></td><td>Transaction: explicit</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>_context.Add()</code></td><td>DB insert side effect</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>_mediator.Publish()</code></td><td>Event side effect (MediatR)</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Background Services</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>: BackgroundService</code></td><td>Background task from ExecuteAsync</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>: IHostedService</code></td><td>Hosted service from StartAsync</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>TimeSpan.FromMinutes(5)</code></td><td>Timer interval</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="my-8 border-t border-gray-800/50"></div>

<h2>Python</h2>

<h3>FastAPI Routes</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@router.get("/path")</code></td><td>GET endpoint with path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@app.post("/path")</code></td><td>POST endpoint</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@router.put</code>, <code>@router.delete</code>, <code>@router.patch</code></td><td>HTTP method + path</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Type-annotated params (<code>user_id: int</code>)</td><td>Path parameters with type</td></tr>
    <tr><td>PascalCase params (<code>item: ItemCreate</code>)</td><td>Request body (Pydantic model)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>Depends(get_current_user)</code></td><td>Security: authentication required</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Return type annotation</td><td>Response body type</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Flask Routes</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@app.route("/path", methods=["GET"])</code></td><td>Endpoint with HTTP method</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@blueprint.route("/path")</code></td><td>Blueprint-based routing</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>methods=["GET", "POST"]</code></td><td>Multiple HTTP methods</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Django REST Framework</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>class UserViewSet(ModelViewSet)</code></td><td>CRUD endpoints (list, create, retrieve, update, destroy)</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@api_view(['GET', 'POST'])</code></td><td>Function-based view with methods</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Models / Entities</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>class User(Base)</code> (SQLAlchemy)</td><td>Entity with <code>__tablename__</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>Column(String, nullable=False)</code></td><td>Field type + constraints</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>relationship("Post")</code></td><td>Relationship to other entity</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>class Article(models.Model)</code> (Django)</td><td>Entity detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>models.CharField(max_length=200)</code></td><td>Field type + max_length constraint</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>models.ForeignKey</code>, <code>ManyToManyField</code></td><td>Relationships</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>class UserCreate(BaseModel)</code> (Pydantic)</td><td>Schema with field types</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>Field(min_length=2, max_length=50)</code></td><td>Validation constraints</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Services + Tasks</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>class UserService</code></td><td>Service detection (name ends in Service/Repository/UseCase)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Public methods (no <code>_</code> prefix)</td><td>Operations with params + return types</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@shared_task</code> / <code>@app.task</code></td><td>Celery task</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@periodic_task</code></td><td>Scheduled task with cron/interval</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="my-8 border-t border-gray-800/50"></div>

<h2>TypeScript / JavaScript</h2>

<h3>Express Routes</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>router.get("/path", handler)</code></td><td>GET endpoint with path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>app.post("/path", handler)</code></td><td>POST endpoint</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>router.put</code>, <code>.delete</code>, <code>.patch</code></td><td>HTTP method + path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>:id</code> in route string</td><td>Path parameter (converted to &#123;id&#125;)</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>NestJS</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@Controller('prefix')</code></td><td>Controller with base path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Get()</code>, <code>@Post()</code>, etc.</td><td>HTTP method + path</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@UseGuards(AuthGuard)</code></td><td>Security: authentication required</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Injectable()</code></td><td>Service detection</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Next.js App Router</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>export async function GET</code></td><td>GET endpoint</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>export async function POST</code></td><td>POST endpoint</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>app/api/users/[id]/route.ts</code></td><td>Path: /api/users/&#123;id&#125;</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3>Entities + Services</h3>
<table>
  <thead><tr><th>Pattern</th><th>What pecto extracts</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td><code>@Entity('table')</code> (TypeORM)</td><td>Entity with table name</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Column()</code>, <code>@PrimaryGeneratedColumn()</code></td><td>Fields with constraints</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@ManyToOne</code>, <code>@OneToMany</code></td><td>Relationships</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>new Schema()</code> (Mongoose)</td><td>Schema detection</td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>@Injectable()</code> / <code>*Service</code> class</td><td>Service with public methods</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="my-8 border-t border-gray-800/50"></div>

<h2>Not extracted (by design)</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Business logic from if/else flows</strong> — too complex for static analysis</li>
  <li><strong>Method-chaining DSLs</strong> — Spring Security filter chains, EF Fluent API, Minimal API</li>
  <li><strong>WPF/XAML</strong> — requires separate XAML parser</li>
  <li><strong>LINQ queries</strong> — complex expression trees</li>
  <li><strong>DI registration</strong> — <code>services.AddScoped&lt;I,T&gt;()</code> chains</li>
  <li><strong>Auth flow detection</strong> — JWT vs Session vs OAuth2 (heuristic, fragile)</li>
</ul>

</DocsLayout>
